(Signal Behavior) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For each matched process:) Tj
T*
(- send SIGTERM) Tj
T*
(- wait up to timeout \(default 5s\)) Tj
T*
(- if still running and force-kill enabled, send SIGKILL) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This is designed to cleanly stop nodes first, then force-stop only when needed.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
